This paper focuses on evaluating and improving the performance of optical flow techniques for facial expression analysis, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques for data augmentation (cs.MM), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and potentially natural language processing (cs.IR) if the paper involves textual data analysis. Finally, the paper may involve statistical analysis and modeling (cs.LG) to evaluate the performance of the optical flow techniques.
